z=f(w)=\frac{1-\sqrt{1-w}}{1+\sqrt{1+w}}, \quad w=\frac{4 z}{(1+z)^{2}}, \quad g(w)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-w}} .
\]

При

\[
f(w)=w, \quad g(w)=(1-w)^{-k-1} .
\]

